    <sec>
      <title>2.3 Evaluation setup</title>
      <p>SCRIBER and the other 7 predictors output both binary (PBR versus non-PBR) and real-valued predictions (propensity for protein binding). We use the evaluation criteria from (<xref rid="btz324-B84" ref-type="bibr">Zhang and Kurgan, 2018</xref>). We assess the binary predictions using sensitivity (SN), specificity (SP), precision (PRE), accuracy (ACC), F1-measure (F1), Matthews correlation coefficient (MCC) and cross-prediction rate (CPR):
